      <h1>Why Viven Is The Video Agency of Choice for B2B Brands</h1>
      <p class="lead">Viven helps B2B brands simplify communication and accelerate sales through tailored video content. Learn how our videos can drive your business forward.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>March 3, 2025</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 24, 2025</span></p>
    </div>
